This repo is an updated version of the version of CUMP in the repo:

https://github.com/skystar0227/CUMP.

See the Changelog file for documentation on what has been changed.

You can generate a local version of the code as follows:

   * autoreconf -i
   * make

You can generate the axpy demo in the demos directory as follows:

   * cd demos
   * make CXX=nvcc
   * ./axpy

